&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s focus on the code on lines 7-30. Here I bundle an API call to our database...I write about my creative route handling &lt;strong&gt;here&lt;/strong&gt;... The returned dataset a list of profiles that is then set in &lt;em&gt;state&lt;/em&gt; using &lt;strong&gt;setProfiles&lt;/strong&gt;. So now that we have those profiles available on the front-end we pass it down to each of the &quot;ProfileHome&quot; Page Components through props.&lt;/p&gt;
